message.body: Going to the farmers market in a little while (you're welcome to join me) and then can do our lesson anytime after that.
Okay, sounds good to me! Are you going to the silver spring one?
I can pick you up if you do want to come

Ah okay...I think I'm going to hold off on the farmers market (major packing mode), but if you don't mind I would need to be picked up for our lesson since our current vehicle is a military tank (and it's parked at bwi) :-\
No problem! When shall I fetch you? I've got designs on the dog park and coffee roasting, but neither of those is time sensitive, and lauren just left for work :p
Gah work on a sunday! My deepest condolences. Do you want to just let me know when you're done at the farmers market and we'll meet up then? My day is also full of non-time-sensitive activities..
Perfect-ill let you know. I'd say about 11-11:30
Delayed by crazy hippie street fair--more like noon
